# Beadcrumbs .gitignore entries
#
# These entries are automatically added by `bdc init`.
# Add them manually if you initialized beadcrumbs without `bdc init`.
#
# Track JSONL files (reasoning data, versioned with code):
#   .beadcrumbs/insights.jsonl
#   .beadcrumbs/threads.jsonl
#   .beadcrumbs/deps.jsonl
#
# Ignore SQLite database (ephemeral, rebuilt from JSONL):

.beadcrumbs/beadcrumbs.db
.beadcrumbs/beadcrumbs.db-journal
.beadcrumbs/beadcrumbs.db-wal
.beadcrumbs/beadcrumbs.db-shm
